### Health check (replace with your real URL)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ords/poc/v1/health

### Create user
POST {{baseUrl}}/ords/poc/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{$guid}}

{
  "email": "ana@example.com",
  "firstName": "Ana",
  "lastName": "Lopez",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Update user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/ords/poc/v1/users/101
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{$guid}}

{
  "firstName": "Ana Maria",
  "lastName": "Lopez",
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

### Invalid payload (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ords/poc/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{$guid}}

{
  "firstName": "NoEmail",
  "lastName": "User"
}
